Package: dell-fanctl
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, python3 (>= 3.10)
Recommends: python3-gi, gir1.2-appindicator3-0.1
Description: Adaptive fan controller for Dell laptops
 Automatically switches between quiet and gaming fan curves based on
 CPU load and temperature. Uses dell_smm_hwmon for direct PWM control.
 .
 Features:
  - Temperature-driven PWM curves with linear interpolation
  - Asymmetric thresholds: fast ramp-up (12s), slow cooldown (30s)
  - System tray applet with manual override
  - Clean shutdown restores BIOS fan control
